{"_id":"2xZY32OeCIpotVAV","name":"Baron Friedrich von Pfeifraucher","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"characteristics":{"ws":{"type":"number","label":"Weapon Skill","abrev":"WS","initial":46,"advances":0,"value":46,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"bs":{"type":"Number","label":"Ballistic Skill","abrev":"BS","initial":38,"advances":0,"value":38,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"s":{"type":"Number","label":"Strength","abrev":"S","initial":27,"advances":0,"value":27,"bonus":2,"cost":25},"t":{"type":"Number","label":"Toughness","abrev":"T","initial":25,"advances":0,"value":25,"bonus":2,"cost":25},"i":{"type":"Number","label":"Initiative","abrev":"I","initial":43,"advances":0,"value":43,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"ag":{"type":"Number","label":"Agility","abrev":"Ag","initial":27,"advances":0,"value":27,"bonus":2,"cost":25},"dex":{"type":"Number","label":"Dexterity","abrev":"Dex","initial":38,"advances":0,"value":38,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"int":{"type":"Number","label":"Intelligence","abrev":"Int","initial":46,"advances":0,"value":46,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"wp":{"type":"Number","label":"Willpower","abrev":"WP","initial":33,"advances":0,"value":33,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"fel":{"type":"Number","label":"Fellowship","abrev":"Fel","initial":52,"advances":0,"value":52,"bonus":5,"cost":25}},"status":{"wounds":{"type":"Number","label":"Wounds","abrev":"W","value":9,"max":9},"advantage":{"type":"Number","label":"Advantage","value":"0","max":10},"criticalWounds":{"type":"Number","label":"Critical Wounds","value":0,"max":2},"sin":{"type":"Number","label":"Sin","value":"0"},"penalties":{"type":"String","label":"Penalties","value":""},"corruption":{"type":"Number","label":"Corruption","value":0},"encumbrance":{"type":"Number","label":"Encumbrance","max":4,"current":0}},"details":{"species":{"type":"String","label":"Species","value":"Human"},"gender":{"type":"String","label":"Gender","value":"Male"},"size":{"type":"String","label":"Size","value":"avg"},"move":{"type":"Number","label":"Movement","value":"4","walk":8,"run":16},"god":{"type":"String","label":"God","value":""},"hitLocationTable":{"value":"hitloc","type":"String","label":"Hit Location Table"},"personal-ambitions":{"short-term":"","long-term":""},"party-ambitions":{"short-term":"","long-term":""},"motivation":{"value":""},"biography":{"value":""},"gmnotes":{"value":"<p><strong>Plot 2 – Compromising Positions</strong></p>\n<p>The @Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.hg1ycyrig5nlt1Ge]{Gravin} is not the only noble in the inn tonight. Also staying there — incognito — is Baron Friedrich von Pfeifraucher, the heir of Count Bruno of Grissenwald. He is accompanied by Fraulein Hanna Lastkahn, a daughter of a wealthy local boat-building family. The two have been conducting an illicit affair for some time, and have taken a room in the inn under the name Herr and Frau Johann Schmidt. Unfortunately, they have been recognised by @Actor[OwcKQuGsjo3UNd0o]{one of Gravin Maria-Ulrike’s servants}, who was once employed in the Pfeifraucher household. A blackmail attempt will follow.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>The ‘Schmidts’ are ‘schmitten’ with each other. For @Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.2xZY32OeCIpotVAV]{Baron Friedrich}, it’s the ninth time he has been in love with an unavailable woman, so he knows it’s real. For @Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.xYDKY1le16R1CfVo]{Fraulein Lastkhan}, she’s in love for the first time, and it’s a love like no one has ever loved before. It’s clear to any who pay attention that Friedrich’s fine manners, noble clothing, and cultured accent are not a natural fit with the name ‘Johann Schmidt’, or with the clearly lower-class ‘Frau Schmidt’.</p>\n<p><strong>Reference:</strong>&nbsp;RNHD p19</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{"autoCalcRun":true,"autoCalcWalk":true,"autoCalcWounds":true,"autoCalcCritW":true,"autoCalcCorruption":true,"autoCalcEnc":true,"modifier":""},"img":"modules/wfrp4e-rnhd/assets/images/tokens/friedrich-von-pfeifraucher.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Johann Schmidt","