{"_id":"a70EXzfG4EI60imu","name":"Bart Fehrwalder","permission":{"default":0},"type":"npc","data":{"characteristics":{"ws":{"type":"number","label":"Weapon Skill","abrev":"WS","initial":34,"advances":0,"value":34,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"bs":{"type":"Number","label":"Ballistic Skill","abrev":"BS","initial":31,"advances":0,"value":31,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"s":{"type":"Number","label":"Strength","abrev":"S","initial":43,"advances":0,"value":43,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"t":{"type":"Number","label":"Toughness","abrev":"T","initial":45,"advances":0,"value":45,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"i":{"type":"Number","label":"Initiative","abrev":"I","initial":44,"advances":0,"value":44,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"ag":{"type":"Number","label":"Agility","abrev":"Ag","initial":38,"advances":0,"value":38,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"dex":{"type":"Number","label":"Dexterity","abrev":"Dex","initial":36,"advances":0,"value":36,"bonus":3,"cost":25},"int":{"type":"Number","label":"Intelligence","abrev":"Int","initial":28,"advances":0,"value":28,"bonus":2,"cost":25},"wp":{"type":"Number","label":"Willpower","abrev":"WP","initial":45,"advances":0,"value":45,"bonus":4,"cost":25},"fel":{"type":"Number","label":"Fellowship","abrev":"Fel","initial":28,"advances":0,"value":28,"bonus":2,"cost":25}},"status":{"wounds":{"type":"Number","label":"Wounds","abrev":"W","value":16,"max":16},"advantage":{"type":"Number","label":"Advantage","value":"0","max":10},"criticalWounds":{"type":"Number","label":"Critical Wounds","value":0,"max":2},"sin":{"type":"Number","label":"Sin","value":"0"},"penalties":{"type":"String","label":"Penalties","value":""},"corruption":{"type":"Number","label":"Corruption","value":0},"encumbrance":{"type":"Number","label":"Encumbrance","max":8,"current":0}},"details":{"species":{"type":"String","label":"Species","value":"Human"},"gender":{"type":"String","label":"Gender","value":"Male"},"size":{"type":"String","label":"Size","value":"avg"},"move":{"type":"Number","label":"Movement","value":"4","walk":8,"run":16},"god":{"type":"String","label":"God","value":""},"hitLocationTable":{"value":"hitloc","type":"String","label":"Hit Location Table"},"personal-ambitions":{"short-term":"","long-term":""},"party-ambitions":{"short-term":"","long-term":""},"motivation":{"value":""},"biography":{"value":""},"gmnotes":{"value":"<p><strong>Plot 5 – Ashes to Ashes</strong></p>\n<p>Some smugglers were expecting to meet a boat, but it scraped a lock in the Vorbergland canals and has lost half a day for repairs. So, the smugglers must hide their cargo in the inn and wait for the boat to arrive in the morning.</p>\n<p>To complicate matters, their contraband is Human: @Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.kONmbNg26XE2LZig]{Josef Aufwiegler}, an agitator wanted for inciting rebellion in Nuln. He was treated with a coma-inducing drug. The smugglers are disguised as a priest and two initiates of Morr, ostensibly taking him home for burial. The drug was timed to wear off once Aufwiegler was safely aboard the boat, but because of the delay he will wake up during the night.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>The ‘Morrians’</strong></p>\n<p>@Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.yhF8vRXDBHziifEX]{Gunni}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.a70EXzfG4EI60imu]{Bart Fehrwalder}, and @Compendium[wfrp4e-rnhd.rnhd-01-3feathers.fJbgFHusP9gP0WxK]{Hans-Frederick Born} are posing as Morrians transporting a body for burial. They are bedecked in paraphernalia they stole from a temple of Morr. They speak only in somewhat theatrical, monotonous tones to maintain their ruse.</p>\n<p>When not posing as Morrians, all three men have high-pitched voices with strong Nulner accents, their tone lifting at the end of every sentence.</p>\n<p><strong>Reference:</strong>&nbsp;RNHD p10, p18</p>"}}},"sort":100001,"flags":{"autoCalcRun":true,"autoCalcWalk":true,"autoCalcWounds":true,"autoCalcCritW":true,"autoCalcCorruption":true,"autoCalcEnc":true,"modifier":"","defensive":0,"talentTests":[],"_sheetTab":"main"},"img":"modules/